            . I am an iron-founder. I work for Messrs. Walter Hunter and Edward Borham, in <placeName id="t18260914-115-crimeloc683">Old Gravel-lane</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18260914-115-crimeloc683" type="placeName" value="Old Gravel-lane"></interp>
