                     <interp inst="t18260914-115-person815" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am the foreman. I found this piece of brass in the waistband of the prisoner's trousers. I said he had been long suspected - he said it was the first he had taken.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. It was a piece of string I took to tie my braces, and here it is now; the foreman said it was the fifth time, and it was the first I had taken.</p>
